Don't miss the launch trailer for Where Winds Meet, an epic Wuxia open world action-adventure game developed by Everstone Studio. Set during the turbulent era of tenth-century China, you take on the role of a young sword master, uncovering forgotten truths and the mysteries of your own identity. As the wind stirs across mountains and rivers, so too will your legend rise.

Where Winds Meet will be available on November 14(PT) for PlayStation 5.

Pre-order and pre-download now!
